body: Select the setup instructions for your device.
The easiest way to learn how to do it, is to work
where one fighter displays the instructions, and the other follows them.

en.serviceTak.step1Description: Quickstart Guide tells you how to start using TAK on your device.
en.serviceTak.step2Description: The Usage Guide tells you how to use the application, according to our standard model.
en.serviceTak.step3Description: Download the Client Package and install it to your TAK device according to the Quickstart Guide, to get using the app.
en.serviceTakUsageCard.title: Purpose
en.serviceTakUsageCard.content:
• Real-time tracking of friendlies (GPS).
  • Send observations to the command post (HQ) for interpretation.
  • Follow the Recon Feed that your command post (HQ) creates for your unit.
